RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: CONTRACT_REF_NO IN (SELECT CONTRACT_REF_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT) AND REFUND_ESN IN (SELECT LATEST_EVENT_SEQ_NO CONTRACT_REF_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT)

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT CONTRACT_REF_NO,USER_REF_NO,BRANCH,CONTRACT_CCY,COUNTERPARTY,TREASURY_SOURCE,BOOK_DATE,DEPARTMENT_CODE,USER_DEFINED_STATUS,LATEST_EVENT_SEQ_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A,LFTBS_CONTRACT_INTEREST B WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REFERENCE_NO AND A.BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND A.MODULE_CODE = 'OL' AND B.SHOWN_IN_CONTRACT_MAIN_SCREEN ='Y' AND EXISTS (SELECT RATE_TYPE FROM LFTBS_CONTRACT_INTEREST WHERE CONTRACT_REFERENCE_NO = B.CONTRACT_REFERENCE_NO AND RATE_TYPE <> 'S' AND EVENT_SEQUENCE_NO = (SELECT MAX(EVENT_SEQUENCE_NO) FROM LFTBS_CONTRACT_INTEREST WHERE CONTRACT_REFERENCE_NO = B.CONTRACT_REFERENCE_NO AND SHOWN_IN_CONTRACT_MAIN_SCREEN ='Y' AND RATE_TYPE <> 'S')) AND A.CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A', 'L') ORDER BY A.CONTRACT_REF_NO

RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_SUMMARY_WHERECLAUSE: BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTB_CONTRACT_REFUND WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = SUMMARYDSN.CONTRACT_REF_NO) and exists (Select 1 From OLVW_USER_ACCESS_PRODUCTS Where PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(SUMMARYDSN.CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND USER_ID = global.user_id)
RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_MULTIBRN_WHERECLAUSE: EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTB_CONTRACT_REFUND WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = SUMMARYDSN.CONTRACT_REF_NO)
